#: 2020-07-30-lockdown-emissions.md:54
#, no-wrap
msgid "Household Pollutants"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-30-lockdown-emissions.md:57
msgid ""
"These can be any number of pollutants: cigarette smoke, fuel for cooking, "
"cleaning sprays, mosquito repellents, or artificial fragrances. They are "
"common and vary around the world."
msgstr ""

